Constant Field Values

FILES_PATH

public static final java.lang.String FILES_PATH
The path under the context path that leads to the exposed files. Slide has /users, /roles, and /files. To enable security, we need to expose /users, which requires files to be exposed through /files, not directly as "". See the scope init_param in web.xml.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

FILES_PATH_WITHOUT_TRAILING

public static final java.lang.String FILES_PATH_WITHOUT_TRAILING
The same path as above, but without the trailing slash. Windows Redirector uses this format. Jetty's SecurityConstraint needs this format to recognize that proper authentication is needed.
